\"hkgmoji\" />, 只係比你臨時楂幾個月"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/exchange-foreign-driving-licence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fexchange-foreign-driving-licence&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM31T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=c2f68115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/exchange-foreign-driving-licence</a><br />\n<br />\nExchange a foreign driving licence<br />\n<br />\nYou can continue to drive in the UK without exchanging your licence for 12 months after becoming resident.<br />\nAfter 12 months you must exchange your licence to keep driving. You can exchange it up to 5 years after becoming resident, if it has not expired.<br />\n<br />\nOrder form D1 from the Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency (DVLA).<br />\n<br />\nSend the form, &pound;43 fee and any documents you need (including your driving licence) to the address on the form.<br />\n<br />\nYou should get your new licence within 3 weeks."},{"pid":"2e4ebf96532b3c611cfbf56f62643408aa1f9136","tid":2294630,"uid":33728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:48:35.000Z","msg":"TD560 上網搵唔到LINK既"},{"pid":"1d956e0d0c9e5e5f014c06f160aeb47253a84e5e","tid":2294630,"uid":129878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a5d87e26048335b1e5549768a7646e962e8e258","tid":2294630,"uid":149662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b40b4f4ded7e753e6fcc87e0b738f0d138909217","tid":2294630,"uid":129878,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"aa49cfd75b54bf5a78b4d826a49e353358fe1dee","tid":2294630,"uid":149662,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:28:32.000Z","msg":"香港可以transfer"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:47:11.000Z","msg":"聽人講有國際牌都要再考架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 只係比你臨時楂幾個月"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/exchange-foreign-driving-licence\" dat